  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released\u00a006/29/2017 1:57PM CT (18:57 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.13-RefurbishTicketLabelBarcodes\">Refurbish Ticket Label Barcodes</h2><p>Refurb ticket labels were not showing/hiding\u00a0a barcode\u00a0based on ticket label settings. This issue has been resolved.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.13-Qpop\u2122AdRotator\">Qpop\u2122Ad Rotator</h2><p>Under some\u00a0conditions the\u00a0Qpop idle screen ad rotator would not begin\u00a0rotating after returning from the ticket summary. This issue has been resolved.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.13-AnnouncementEmails\">Announcement Emails</h2><p>The Email and Dashboard display rules were not always enforced properly. Now email notifications will be sent\u00a0when email is included, and announcements will show on the dashboard when the dashboard view is included.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.13-ReportCatalogItemSearches\">Report Catalog Item Searches</h2><p>Special characters in the catalog item search no longer\u00a0prevent the report from filtering properly.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.13-LocationOverridesExport\">Location Overrides Export</h2><p>The location overrides export has been optimized. When exporting\u00a0dozens or hundreds of locations worth of location overrides, the export will now succeed without\u00a0 reaching memory limits.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.12.13-CustomFormHTMLField\">Custom Form HTML Field</h2><p>Submitting multiple edits at different times on a custom form that has an HTML field with formatting would sometimes duplicate the HTML formatting (e.g. bullet lists) with each edit. This issue has been resolved, and formatting will remain consistent through multiple edits.</p>",
